{
  "stem": "18778.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the was to sail on May 13th, 1939, so my parents had me come back to Rheydt about a week, a week and a half earlier so I could say goodbye to my friends who were still there-- meanwhile, quite a few had left already-- and-- and so that we would then be together.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the plan was to go to Berlin to say goodbye to my mother's sister and her family and my grandmother, who was then living in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she had stayed in Berlin permanently after our house had been vandalized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took the train to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never saw the city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were there for about three days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I have an autograph book in which everybody wrote.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whenever I want to cry I look at that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And from there, we took the train to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were-- we arrived in Hamburg probably the day before embarkation, on the 12th.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother's sister came with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The other sister had already emigrated to Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was no longer in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by the way, the Nazis were agreeable that all those Orthodox Jews were allowed to embark already on Fridays, because of the religious law of not being allowed to ride on Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If they were ensconced on the ship before Shabbat, that was OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We embarked on Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We stayed in a hotel, in a nice hotel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we weren't allowed to eat in the dining room there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a sign, Jews, Jews are not-- [GERMAN], which means Jews are not-- I wouldn't even say 'permitted,' but we do not wish Jews to come here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we ate somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
